<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="雜科聲德" xml:id="gsz0891b20shiDaoWu"><lb
ed="T" n="0891b20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0891b20"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>溫州陶山<persName key="A013869">道晤</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0891b21"/><persName key="A013869">釋道晤</persName>者，不知何許人也。高趣放蕩，識量<lb
ed="T" n="0891b22"/>難貲。末住<placeName key="PL000000012592">永嘉陶山</placeName>側精舍，則<persName key="A004531">隱居</persName>修《真<lb
ed="T" n="0891b23"/>誥》之所也。<date key="j20011912005747" notAfter-iso="+0779-06-13" notBefore-iso="+0766-12-22"><name>大曆</name>中</date>，<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>為<persName key="A004531">陶真君</persName>樹此精<lb
ed="T" n="0891b24"/>舍，<persName key="A013869">晤</persName>於此進修靡怠，人亦傾仰。一夕<anchor xml:id="beg0891002"/>跏<anchor xml:id="end0891002"/>趺<lb
ed="T" n="0891b25"/>而卒，身肉無沮，如入三昧，議不焚葬。後五<lb
ed="T" n="0891b26"/>年，忽舉右手，狀若傳香。州官民庶異之，以<lb
ed="T" n="0891b27"/>事奏，勅賜紫袈裟，諡曰<persName key="A013869">實相大師</persName>。至今塔<lb
ed="T" n="0891b28"/>中，州民祈禱，<anchor xml:id="beg0891sgsz5"/>旛華<anchor xml:id="end0891sgsz5"/>填委焉。</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0891b2901"><lb
ed="T" n="0891b29"/>系曰：凡諸入滅舉其指者，蓋示其得四沙<pb ed="T" n="0891c" xml:id="T50.2061.0891c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0891c01"/>門果之數也。昔<persName key="A000218">求那跋摩</persName>舉<anchor xml:id="beg0891sgsz7"/>二<anchor xml:id="end0891sgsz7"/>指而滅，言<lb
ed="T" n="0891c02"/>已證二果歟？其次<persName key="A006171">法京</persName>垂滅，屈三指。<persName key="A005877">慧景</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0891c03"/>反握二指，捋之還屈。今<persName key="A013869">晤</persName>之伸指，豈不同<lb
ed="T" n="0891c04"/>諸？</p>
